ا"},{"b":"1.3","h":"1.5","c":"ٱلۡقَٰسِطُونَ","d":"l-qāsiṭūna","e":"the unjust","i":"الۡقٰسِطُوۡنَ"},{"b":"2.7","h":"3.78","c":"فَكَانُواْ","d":"fakānū","e":"they will be","i":"فَكَانُوۡا"},{"b":"3.7","h":"5.52","c":"لِجَهَنَّمَ","d":"lijahannama","e":"for Hell","i":"لِجَهَنَّمَ"},{"b":"5.4","h":"7.78","c":"حَطَبٗا","d":"ḥaṭaban","e":"firewood","i":"حَطَبًاۙ"}],"a":{"g":"But as for the unjust, they will be, for Hell, firewood.'"}},"16":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.9","c":"وَأَلَّوِ","d":"wa-allawi","e":"And if","i":"وَّاَنْ لَّوِ"},{"b":"0.93","h":"2.21","c":"ٱسۡتَقَٰمُواْ","d":"is'taqāmū","e":"they had remained","i":"اسۡتَقَامُوۡا"},{"b":"2.2","h":"4.23","c":"عَلَى","d":"ʿalā","e":"on","i":"عَلَى"},{"b":"2.5","h":"4.99","c":"ٱلطَّرِيقَةِ","d":"l-ṭarīqati","e":"the Way","i":"الطَّرِيۡقَةِ"},{"b":"3.7","h":"6.96","c":"لَأَسۡقَيۡنَٰهُم","d":"la-asqaynāhum","e":"surely We (would) have given them to drink","i":"لَاَسۡقَيۡنٰهُمۡ"},{"b":"6.4","h":"10.21","c":"مَّآءً","d":"māan","e":"water","i":"مَّآءً"},{"b":"8.6","h":"12.1","c":"غَدَقٗا","d":"ghadaqan","e":"(in) abundance","i":"غَدَقًاۙ"}],"a":{"g":"And [Allah revealed] that if they had remained straight on the way, We would have given them abundant provision"}},"17":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.7","c":"لِّنَفۡتِنَهُمۡ","d":"linaftinahum","e":"That We might test them","i":"لِّنَفۡتِنَهُمۡ"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.86","c":"فِيهِۚ","d":"fīhi","e":"therein","i":"فِيۡهِؕ"},{"b":"3.6","h":"5.7","c":"وَمَن","d":"waman","e":"And whoever","i":"وَمَنۡ"},{"b":"5.0","h":"7.14","c":"يُعۡرِضۡ","d":"yuʿ'riḍ","e":"turns away","i":"يُّعۡرِضۡ"},{"b":"5.6","h":"8.24","c":"عَن","d":"ʿan","e":"from","i":"عَنۡ"},{"b":"6.6","h":"9.28","c":"ذِكۡرِ","d":"dhik'ri","e":"the Remembrance","i":"ذِكۡرِ"},{"b":"7.1","h":"10.17","c":"رَبِّهِۦ","d":"rabbihi","e":"(of) his Lord","i":"رَبِّهٖ"},{"b":"8.0","h":"11.88","c":"يَسۡلُكۡهُ","d":"yasluk'hu","e":"He will make him enter","i":"يَسۡلُكۡهُ"},{"b":"9","h":"13.38","c":"عَذَابٗا","d":"ʿadhāban","e":"a punishment","i":"عَذَابًا"},{"b":"10.5","h":"15.42","c":"صَعَدٗا","d":"ṣaʿadan","e":"severe","i":"صَعَدًاۙ"}],"a":{"g":"So We might test them therein. And whoever turns away from the remembrance of his Lord He will put into arduous punishment."}},"18":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1.05","c":"وَأَنَّ","d":"wa-anna","e":"And that","i":"وَّاَنَّ"},{"b":"1.3","h":"2.34","c":"ٱلۡمَسَٰجِدَ","d":"l-masājida","e":"the masajid","i":"الۡمَسٰجِدَ"},{"b":"2.6","h":"4.26","c":"لِلَّهِ","d":"lillahi","e":"(are) for Allah","i":"لِلّٰهِ"},{"b":"3.5","h":"5.73","c":"فَلَا","d":"falā","e":"so (do) not","i":"فَلَا"},{"b":"4.1","h":"6.65","c":"تَدۡعُواْ","d":"tadʿū","e":"call","i":"تَدۡعُوۡا"},{"b":"4.9","h":"8.07","c":"مَعَ","d":"maʿa","e":"with","i":"مَعَ"},{"b":"5.3","h":"8.7","c":"ٱللَّهِ","d":"l-lahi","e":"Allah","i":"اللّٰهِ"},{"b":"6.0","h":"9.98","c":"أَحَدٗا","d":"aḥadan","e":"anyone","i":"اَحَدًاۙ"}],"a":{"g":"And [He revealed] that the masjids are for Allah, so do not invoke with Allah anyone."}},"19":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.6","c":"وَأَنَّهُۥ","d":"wa-annahu","e":"And that","i":"وَّاَنَّهٗ"},{"b":"1.8","h":"2.81","c":"لَمَّا","d":"lammā","e":"when","i":"لَمَّا"},{"b":"3.0","h":"4.42","c":"قَامَ","d":"qāma","e":"stood up","i":"قَامَ"},{"b":"3.5","h":"5.27","c":"عَبۡدُ","d":"ʿabdu","e":"(the) slave","i":"عَبۡدُ"},{"b":"4.2","h":"6.46","c":"ٱللَّهِ","d":"l-lahi","e":"(of) Allah","i":"اللّٰهِ"},{"b":"4.9","h":"7.68","c":"يَدۡعُوهُ","d":"yadʿūhu","e":"calling (upon) Him","i":"يَدۡعُوۡهُ"},{"b":"5.8","h":"9.25","c":"كَادُواْ","d":"kādū","e":"they almost","i":"كَادُوۡا"},{"b":"6.7","h":"10.62","c":"يَكُونُونَ","d":"yakūnūna","e":"became","i":"يَكُوۡنُوۡنَ"},{"b":"7.7","h":"12.44","c":"عَلَيۡهِ","d":"ʿalayhi","e":"around him","i":"عَلَيۡهِ"},{"b":"8.6","h":"13.96","c":"لِبَدٗا","d":"libadan","e":"a compacted mass","i":"لِبَدًاؕ"}],"a":{"g":"And that when the Servant of Allah stood up supplicating Him, they almost became about him a compacted mass.\""}},"20":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.35","c":"قُلۡ","d"