 know if what you are promised is near or if my Lord will grant for it a [long] period.\""}},"26":{"w":[{"b":"0.05","h":"0.55","c":"عَٰلِمُ","d":"ʿālimu","e":"(The) All-Knower","i":"عٰلِمُ"},{"b":"0.84","h":"1.79","c":"ٱلۡغَيۡبِ","d":"l-ghaybi","e":"(of) the unseen","i":"الۡغَيۡبِ"},{"b":"1.6","h":"2.94","c":"فَلَا","d":"falā","e":"so not","i":"فَلَا"},{"b":"2.2","h":"4.04","c":"يُظۡهِرُ","d":"yuẓ'hiru","e":"He reveals","i":"يُظۡهِرُ"},{"b":"3.0","h":"5.19","c":"عَلَىٰ","d":"ʿalā","e":"from","i":"عَلٰى"},{"b":"3.5","h":"6.31","c":"غَيۡبِهِۦٓ","d":"ghaybihi","e":"His unseen","i":"غَيۡبِهٖۤ"},{"b":"6.0","h":"9.07","c":"أَحَدًا","d":"aḥadan","e":"(to) anyone","i":"اَحَدًاۙ"}],"a":{"g":"[He is] Knower of the unseen, and He does not disclose His [knowledge of the] unseen to anyone"}},"27":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.25","c":"إِلَّا","d":"illā","e":"Except","i":"اِلَّا"},{"b":"0.79","h":"1.36","c":"مَنِ","d":"mani","e":"whom","i":"مَنِ"},{"b":"1.1","h":"1.85","c":"ٱرۡتَضَىٰ","d":"ir'taḍā","e":"He has approved","i":"ارۡتَضٰى"},{"b":"2.0","h":"3.46","c":"مِن","d":"min","e":"of","i":"مِنۡ"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.67","c":"رَّسُولٖ","d":"rasūlin","e":"a Messenger","i":"رَّسُوۡلٍ"},{"b":"4.1","h":"6.23","c":"فَإِنَّهُۥ","d":"fa-innahu","e":"and indeed, He","i":"فَاِنَّهٗ"},{"b":"5.8","h":"8.56","c":"يَسۡلُكُ","d":"yasluku","e":"makes to march","i":"يَسۡلُكُ"},{"b":"6.7","h":"9.87","c":"مِنۢ","d":"min","e":"from","i":"مِنۡۢ"},{"b":"7.5","h":"10.98","c":"بَيۡنِ","d":"bayni","e":"before","i":"بَيۡنِ"},{"b":"8.0","h":"11.88","c":"يَدَيۡهِ","d":"yadayhi","e":"him","i":"يَدَيۡهِ"},{"b":"8.9","h":"13.17","c":"وَمِنۡ","d":"wamin","e":"and from","i":"وَمِنۡ"},{"b":"9.4","h":"14.06","c":"خَلۡفِهِۦ","d":"khalfihi","e":"behind him","i":"خَلۡفِهٖ"},{"b":"10.4","h":"15.71","c":"رَصَدٗا","d":"raṣadan","e":"a guard","i":"رَصَدًاۙ"}],"a":{"g":"Except whom He has approved of messengers, and indeed, He sends before each messenger and behind him observers"}},"28":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.55","c":"لِّيَعۡ